ling to meet their quotas.<\/li>\n<li>   Mind your manners! You&#8217;ll get a lot farther by being calm and pleasant than you will by being angry and defensive. (It&#8217;s okay to feel angry and defensive. Just don&#8217;t let them know!)<\/li>\n<li>If you have a lump sum to offer, start low and let them talk you up. (I told one person I had $3,500 and wound up settling for $4,100.)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">I&#8217;m proud of you Kim!!!  Lets keep from getting back into debt now, eh ;)<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fighting the collection agencies? My girl Kim (aka Little Miss Fortune) just put out a brilliant piece on how to settle and save BIG! $14,000&#8230; <\/p>\n<p class=\"more\"><a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/how-to-beat-collection-agencies\/\">Read More<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":15691,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[74,98],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-547","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-advice","category-debt"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v24.6 (Yoast SEO v24.5) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>How To Beat The Collection Agencies! | Budgets Are Sexy<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/how-to-beat-collection-agencies\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"How To Beat The Collection Agencies! | Budgets Are Sexy\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Fighting the collection agencies? My girl Kim (aka Little Miss Fortune)